{"tid":831862,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【AA搶客搶到顛】屯門新盤 情侶路過也中槍","createTime":"2018-09-22T10:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T03:28:22.000Z","uid":122377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cc3663607e0f67b567a77e180e2e4703d5393ab3","tid":831862,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:28:02.000Z","msg":"中資萬科旗下屯門山旯旮新盤上源昨日開價，首批231伙，當中最平呎價不足萬元，成為近一年內呎價最平新盤。項目設於長沙灣的售樓廠，今日為首個開放的周末，下午兩點左右，售樓廠現場有近百人排隊睇樓。<br />\n<br />\n由於下午上源售樓廠一帶有大批代理推銷，現場偶爾出現代理爭客情景，一對年輕男女路過售樓廠門口，被大約十名代理一湧而上包圍著，即時有人起哄叫囂，該名女子被數人互相推撞，更被撞到垃圾筒旁邊，場面混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180922/58711784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180922%2F58711784&d=ApFr65%2F7CQXVI7Zo3g%2FMeTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=05fd9c57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180922%2F58711784&h=43535ccc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180922/58711784</a><br />\n<br />\n條片笑撚到仆街 班AA餓左幾撚耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ebbe356e790f2f59317f14e909cbd1c2f0122a","tid":831862,"uid":15184,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:52:05.000Z","msg":"成班好似餓狗搶屎咁 真係笑撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b585d982ca5a93a2b6d6660f85526b9daa50a5a","tid":831862,"uid":190818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T12:00:05.000Z","msg":"好厹feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 餓到咁"},{"pid":"9468e3ae393df55e323736acca84f5e5d94e64d1","tid":831862,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:28:22.000Z","msg":"成班黑社會咁既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/